Header 1: This is a CSV file. COMMAS ARE PROHIBITED.
Header Two: To learn how to import a CSV into Markdown please read [the source file.](https://github.com/FlarosOverfield/Zeitgeist/blob/trainer/Markdown.md) It's quite complicated but easily copy-pasteable.

Header 1: Folder containing CSV files MUST be named _data.
Header Two: Nothing else will be read. Not even _Data or _files.
This is a Toku Kun. You can type markdown in a CSV file and it will render correctly as long as you don't use commas quotes bars or tabs. Which is kind of insane.
